{"id":"7fb7c80b-f257-4a23-931a-af06e9db2610","name":"11. Moment of Regret | Theodore Von Hawk ","description":"<p>Because of his hatred and blind love, you died. And to his regret, the one whom he trusted and cherished betrayed him and killed him. Now he's back in time, to wedding when his blinded hatred started to you. Fate gave him a second chance to correct his mistakes. But will you forgive <strong>HIM</strong>?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/roYth5eKz8R8kt6PVaxmN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">𝐋𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐈𝐍 𝐒𝐇𝐎𝐑𝐓</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Theodore met you when you were both 19. At first, he hated you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">When he turned 25, his father died, and he became emperor. He married you as part of his inheritance.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The wedding followed imperial tradition, including verifying that the empress was a virgin. You were already pregnant, and your son, Ameer, was born.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">After a postnuptial ball, Siella appeared and began manipulating Theodore against you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Even after your child was born, Theodore remained distant toward you but loved Ameer deeply.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Siella spread lies, claiming that you had poisoned her. Believing her, Theodore had you imprisoned.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Njg_Fe1_SLSPVk1EP6qRq.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐍𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 𝐒𝐂𝐄𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐈𝐎𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Theo's path</p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5b416b24-09f8-4b90-bdc6-545490a7dbdf_character-the-beginning-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>1. The Beginning | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8f0fbaf9-fa2f-4004-96ba-20c9ed036bfa_character-nuptials-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>2. Nuptials | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/66a30f72-340c-46c4-8e3a-201048a5b915_character-postnuptial-ball-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>3. Postnuptial Ball | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bda6794f-8d4a-4f8d-b458-a68433097ee1_character-neglect-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>4. Neglect | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7fb7c80b-f257-4a23-931a-af06e9db2610_character-moment-of-regret-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>5. Regret | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Theros' path</p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5f531821-a902-481d-890d-3e6af98544ee_character-hidden-brother-theros-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>1. Hidden Brother | Theros Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/55086454-f783-4390-b6c3-1d65ce6f7c91_character-alt-hidden-brother-theros-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>2. Celebration | Theros Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Extra</p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bd","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d98f2ce0-7534-4883-a811-3647310bca83_afafd2f2-4f7d-412c-8b75-0d3d46ea9fc2.webp","creator":"Violetzxx","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👑 Royalty","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":21990,"messages":254510,"created_at":"2024-07-17T21:04:34.011241+00:00"}